data.description: Great opportunity with instant equity!  This inviting 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom mountain home has all of the modern amenities inside and peaceful setting outside ! Wonderful 1.15 acre heavily treed corner lot a tranquil creek running along side the property. Gorgeous, bright upper level living space has ample windows, stanning vaulted ceilings, fireplace, dining area, and hardwood flooring.  Updated upper level bathroom with claw foot tub and hammered copper sink.  Lower level has large game room/den, 2nd bedroom, updated 3/4 bathroom and utility room. Newer windows, furnace, tankless water heater, well pump, and filtration system. Enjoy the serenity of the mountains while being only 40 minutes from Denver, and 30 minutes from Boulder & Golden.  A little elbow grease on the exterior will go a long way, don’t miss this amazing opportunity! Property is in need of a new roof, paint and decking on front porch and is being sold being sold as is.
